name: UNDENIABLE
description:
UNDENIABLE

There will be no later or any memories.
This time is perfect.
Even I’d rather die in your lap though.
My hopes and goals are accomplished at this time. Don’t fuse my happiness with your fear.
Just be brave enough to deliver yourself for me.
Completely. 


Watercolor on paper 200gsm
3561 × 3600 px
Translated by: Aini Wilinsen
